{
  "stem": "9156.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He told me about the horrible treatment he got in his own family.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He was the youngest of the 12 children of his older sister, because his parents were dead.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Whatever happened, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And so I felt very close to his history.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I felt with him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We could talk to each other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "On the other hand, he was a man who was always very angry.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "When he got mad, he would yell and hit anybody who was around.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I have often thought about it, how strange it is that I don't remember being hit very much.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But I still remember Ruth being hit, Hannah being hit, my mother being hit.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And he was yelling.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He was loud.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this is my parents.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it's-- I could tell for hours about them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mother told me about her story, because I was a curious child.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I always asked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Otherwise, I wouldn't know anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have to say, Mother came from Prczmyl, P-R-C-Z-M-Y-L.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, it's a difficult-- and she was-- they were poor, too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But she was very proud of her family because her grandfather was a writer of the Torah.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you had to be very good to do that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But at the same time, she lost her mother very early and there was a stepmother who was very angry at having all these little kids running around.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my mother was playing, because she liked balls-- she still-- I still never forget that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She pressed the dry raspberries in her hands and threw them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they stuck at the ceiling.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And from then on she was forbidden to go to school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So Mother had-- I don't know how many, a few years of schooling.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I want to say that this woman, all her life, has read voluminously.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
